"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-06-heartbroken-team-gb-star-lina-nielsen-consoled-reporter-falling-olympic-hurdles-21374507\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GB star Lina Nielsen broke down in tears and opened up on her battle with multiple sclerosis after she fell in the semi-finals of the women's 400m hurdles at theParisOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.6837484208957255, \"rank\": 0.4622102544712986, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 25, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lina_Nielsen\", \"score\": 0.9999991703906548, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lina Nielsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lina_Nielsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lina_Nielsen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nielsen had ambitions of making tomorrow night's showpiece but the 28-year-old's dreams went up in smoke as she clattered into the final barrier of the opening semi-final.\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brit was able to return to her feet and eventually crossed the finish line in last place with time of 1:31.22, with Jamaica's Rushell Clayton and the USA's Jasmine Jones progressing in first and second.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.976363253029461, \"rank\": 0.024204425974954733, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 485, \"end\": 500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rushell_Clayton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rushell Clayton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rushell_Clayton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rushell_Clayton\"}, {\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6465151167820316, \"rank\": 0.54345744961596, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\", \"score\": 0.9999999996534825, \"rank\": 3.1199554205045474e-10, \"text\": \"Jasmine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pictures showed a dejected and fatigued Nielsen close to tears, with the disappointment of the situation clearly beginning to set in at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"score\": 0.9999567335109227, \"rank\": 2.5382270588176155e-05, \"text\": \"Nielsen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\"}, {\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow\\u00a0Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris Olympics 2024  The defending Olympic champion, Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone, advanced from the second semi-final and\\u00a0will do battle with Femke Bol - the reigning world champion - in what promises to be a thrilling showdown in the French capital  Speaking just moments after her fall, Nielsen said she 'really believed' she could book a spot in the final before revealing the concerns she had for her health in the build-up to the race.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 826, \"end\": 832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999373202776425, \"rank\": 5.354381808288258e-05, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 913, \"end\": 922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Femke_Bol\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Femke Bol\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Femke_Bol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Femke_Bol\"}, {\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9595664641824047, \"rank\": 0.028872667753841084, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1060, \"end\": 1067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"score\": 0.9999567335109227, \"rank\": 2.5382270588176155e-05, \"text\": \"Nielsen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes after Nielsen went public with her MS diagnosis after suffering a relapse two days prior to the heats at the 2022 World Athletics Championships in Oregon.\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"score\": 0.9999567335109227, \"rank\": 2.5382270588176155e-05, \"text\": \"Nielsen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\"}, {\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.9978052579633404, \"rank\": 0.0015836350539776426, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Heartbreak for Lina Nielsen \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0092\\u0094#BBCOlympics#Paris2024#Olympicspic.twitter.com/bjDxrNjFzJ  'I am fighting every single day to try and get here.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lina_Nielsen\", \"score\": 0.9999991703906548, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lina Nielsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lina_Nielsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lina_Nielsen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really believed I could make the final which was why I was really fighting,' Nielsen told Eurosport.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"score\": 0.9999567335109227, \"rank\": 2.5382270588176155e-05, \"text\": \"Nielsen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's just disappointing it had to end that way.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would have loved to end on a personal best.\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'To tell you the truth, I was panicking all week because I thought being in the village and being around so many people and Covid and the food\\u2026 I was scared that I might suffer another relapse.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are so proud of you@LinaFJNielsen\\u00e2\\u009d\\u00a4\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008f\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0092\\u00ac \\\"10 years ago I had to learn how to walk again\\\"#WhereItStarts|#Paris2024|#Athleticspic.twitter.com/ktxgiAaIQV  'The last time I was at a major championships I could not even make it past the heats so I have to be somewhat proud that I made it to the semi-finals and I will take that disappointment onto the rest of the season.'\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Radzi Chinyanganya, working for Eurosport, offered his support and an arm around the shoulder after Nielsen's emotions rose to the surface once again.\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2293, \"end\": 2311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radzi_Chinyanganya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Radzi Chinyanganya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radzi_Chinyanganya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radzi_Chinyanganya\"}, {\"begin\": 2393, \"end\": 2400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"score\": 0.9999567335109227, \"rank\": 2.5382270588176155e-05, \"text\": \"Nielsen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's been tough.\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ten years ago I had to learn how to walk again,' Nielsen said before putting her head in her hands.\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2512, \"end\": 2519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"score\": 0.9999567335109227, \"rank\": 2.5382270588176155e-05, \"text\": \"Nielsen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the Eurosport studio, Iwan Thomas heaped praise on Nielsen for the mental and physical resilience she had shown in making it to the semi-finals of an Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2589, \"end\": 2600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iwan_Thomas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Iwan Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iwan_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iwan_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"score\": 0.9999567335109227, \"rank\": 2.5382270588176155e-05, \"text\": \"Nielsen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She's had to learn how to walk again so you think how proud her family must be of her and how proud she should be,' the former 400m runner said.\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'She has made an Olympic Games semi-final and unfortunately fell, but this is an athlete who was probably not given the hope of being an athlete anymore.'\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 3034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Matthew Hudson-Smith's mum breaks hearts everywhere as she wipes away Team GB star's tears after 400m final  ArrowMORE:French pole vaulter reacts to the buzz around penis that ended his Olympic dream  ArrowMORE:14-year-old Olympian reveals unusual gift from parents after winning gold in Paris  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\",